    "title": "京东开放平台钟表眼镜类目资质标准",
    "followRuleId": "673347981335990272",
    "content": "<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"margin-left: -.5pt; background: white; border-collapse: collapse; border: none;\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height: 17.5pt;\">\n<td style=\"border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; background: #C00000; padding: 0cm 5.4pt 0cm 5.4pt; height: 17.5pt;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">特殊资质及要求</span></strong></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">1. <span style=\"color: #000000; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 13.3333px; text-align: left; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff; float: none; display: inline;\">入驻旗舰店和卖场店开放TM标入驻且TM标申请时间至入驻审核时间必须大于6个月</span> </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">，专卖店和专营店开放TM标入驻开店（注册申请时间至开店审核时间必须大于3个月），TM标有效期请填写申请日期+2年后的日期，R标有效期按商标注册证有效日期填写。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">专卖店、专营店需有3级以内（包括3级）的完整授权链路。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">委托进口协议（经营进口商品）：报关单上的收货人和消费使用单位不在授权链上，需提供委托报关授权。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">报关单（经营进口商品）：近3年内的中华人民共和国海关进口货物报关单，报关单上应展现对应品牌名称及商品名称。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">5. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">经营框架类有度数眼镜（近视、远视）的商家，需提交验光人员职业资格证书以及验光设备焦度计、验光仪的年度检定证书。</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height: 102.0pt;\">\n<td style=\"border: solid windowtext 1.0pt; border-top: none; padding: 0cm 0cm 0cm 0cm; height: 102.0pt;\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">旗舰店授权书模板：</span><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/926-4279.html\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">旗舰店授权书模板</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">卖场店授权书模板：</span><a href=\"https://helpcenter.jd.com/vender/issue/1000-44485.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">卖场店授权模板</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东开放平台各类目资费一览表：</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=638209647311982592&amp;type=0&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">京东开放平台类目资费规则</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt 6.5pt; line-height: 200%; background: white; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">店铺命</span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">名规则：</span><a href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: blue;\">https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=2598</span></a></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">附则</span></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东商家的行为，发生在本管理规则生效之日以前的，适用当时的规则。发生在本管理规则生效之日以后的，适用本规则。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">京东可根据平台运营情况随时调整本管理规则并以公告的形式向商家公示。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">商家应遵守国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件。对任何涉嫌违反国家法律、行政法规、部门规章等规范性文件的行为，本规则已有规定的，适用于本规则。本规则尚无规定的，京东有权酌情处理。但京东对商家的处理不免除其应承担的法律责任。商家在京东的任何行为，应同时遵守与京东及其关联公司签订的各项协议。</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left; line-height: 200%; background: white; margin: 0cm 0cm 0.0001pt; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"left\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4. </span><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">本规则标准于2025年3月3日修订，于2025年3月10日生效。</span></p>",
